p: Transmission was detected in all Anopheles species and Ae. aegypti (albeit very poorly), but not in Cx. quinquefasciatus. An. gambiae, An. quadrimaculatus and An. stephensi were able to transmit both MAYV strains tested. For Ae. aegypti only a single transmission event was detected for virus strain BeAr 505411. Only virus strain BeAn 343102 was transmitted by An. freeborni. Both virus strains could be transmitted by An. gambiae, quadrimaculatus and stephensi.
